text: Day ur twalav ara win inumren Iboahim $ef Mass is, acku Ifka yas Oebbi tagelda? Mi inna Iboahim: "Mass iw d win Issidiren, Ineqqen", inna d: "nek ssidire$, neqqe$". Inna Iboahim: "ihi, Oebbi Issenqao ed iiij seg ugmuv; kecc, ssenqeo it id seg utaram"! Inneecam win ijehlen. Oebbi ur Inehhu yara agdud imednas
